= Ishbel MacDonald

Ishbel is the eldest daughter of Ramsay MacDonald. She's currently studying social sciences at university but because of her father's widower status, could be expected to become official hostess at Downing Street if he were to ever take office.

- @emergency_fundraising
- @welfare
- @organizing_women
