@emergency_fundraising
title: Emergency Fundraising
subtitle: An emergency infusion of resources.
view-if: difficulty < 1
choose-if: advisor_action_timer = 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; resources += dues

We have gained +[+ dues +] resources.

@welfare
title: Support Workers' Welfare, our mutual aid organization.
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources > 0 and advisor_action_timer = 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?][? if resources < 0: Not enough resources. ?]
on-arrival: resources -= 1; workers_aid += 1; unemployed_labour += 5*(1 - dissent); workers_labour += 3*(1-dissent); workers_labour += 2*(1-dissent) if black_thursday_seen; advisor_action_timer = 6;

We have increased funding to Workers' Welfare. [? if black_thursday_seen > 0 : In an age of economic crisis, this will be helpful for improving our standing among the unemployed. ?]

@organizing_women
title: Organizing women
subtitle: Ishbel's charm could help Labour to appeal to more "traditional" women.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer = 0 and labour_in_government
unavailable-subtitle: [? if not labour_in_government: Labour is not in government. ?] [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: womens_rights += 1; workers_labour += 4*(1-dissent); rural_labour += 3*(1-dissent); old_middle_labour += 3*(1-dissent); advisor_action_timer = 6

Ishbel's strategies for organizing women are aimed at working-class housewives, and acknowledge women's traditional household roles. We argue that our economic welfare programs will improve the livelihoods of women and their families.

[? if labour_r < 50 : Unfortunately, women still disproportionately support the bourgeois parties. ?]

